(amụrụ na Julaị 21, 1992), nke a maara dịka Dash (nke a na-akpọ Da$H), bụ ónyé America na-eti egwu
Ewezuga ọrụ ya n'onwe ya, Dash bụ ónyé otu Heir Global, n'akụkụ enyi na onye na-arụkọ ọrụ, Retch
Dash bụkwa ónyé mmekọ nke ASAP Mob, na-eme ka ọ pụta ìhè mbụ ya na mixtape mbụ ha Lords Never Worry, na 2012
Ọ na-arụkọ ọrụ ugboro ugboro na onye na-emepụta ihe ndekọ Mordecai Beats, ónyé ya na ya wepụtara mixtape La Cienega (2012)
Da$h esorola ọtụtụ ndị rapper a ma ama na ụlọ ọrụ hip-hop rụkọọ ọrụ, gụnyere Ab-Soul, Action Bronson, Earl Sweatshirt, Vince Staples na Mac Miller.
